|text = {{{message|{{{1|This user}}} is {{{descriptor|busy}}} {{{2|in [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Real_life Real Life]}}} {{#if:{{{end|}}}|until&nbsp;{{{end}}}&nbsp;}}{{#if:{{{reason|}}}|due to&nbsp;{{{reason}}}&nbsp;}}and may not respond swiftly to queries.{{#if:{{{msg|}}}|<P>{{{msg}}} }} }}}
| style     = {{#if:{{{width|}}}|width: {{{width}}}px;}} {{#ifeq:{{{shadow}}}|yes|{{box-shadow|0px|2px|4px|rgba(0,0,0,0.2)}}|}}
}}<noinclude>{{documentation}}<!---If anyone can find a better picture, please do so!---></noinclude>

{{Documentation subpage}}

=== Usage ===
Use on user pages or user talk pages when people shouldn't expect them to be answered to quickly. When using simply <code><nowiki>{{busy}}</nowiki></code>, the template produces the message above

=== Parameters ===

There are two unnamed parameters. The first which replaces "this user" with the name placed.<br>
IE <code><nowiki>{{busy|He}}</nowiki></code> produces
{{busy|He}}
The second unnamed parameter replaces "in real life" with whatever is put. Unfortunately, at the time being it requires for there to be something in the first parameter (DO NOT use <nowiki>{{busy||foo}}</nowiki>).<br>
IE <code><nowiki>{{busy|This user|at school}}</nowiki></code> produces
{{busy|This user|at school}}

=== Optional parameters ===

*'''reason''', use to specify a reason why you will be busy.<br>
IE <code><nowiki>{{busy|reason=not being allowed to edit Wikibooks while at work,}}</nowiki></code> produces
{{busy|reason=not being allowed to edit Wikibooks while at work,}}
*'''end''', use to specify until when you will be busy.<br>
IE <code><nowiki>{{busy|end=Monday evening (UTC)}}</nowiki></code> produces
{{busy|end=Monday evening (UTC)}}
*'''msg''' appends any custom message at the end.<br>
IE <code><nowiki>{{busy|msg=April Fool!}}</nowiki></code> produces
{{busy|msg=April Fool!}}
*'''small''' will display the small version of this box,<br>
IE <code><nowiki>{{busy|small=yes}}</nowiki></code> produces
{{busy|small=yes}}

{{-}}
=== Sample using all parameters ===
<code><nowiki>{{busy|Johnny Doe|at school|reason=school being compulsory|end=Saturday morning (EST)|msg=I won't be on for Saturday the 25th, though.}}</nowiki></code> produces

{{busy|Johnny Doe|at school|reason=school being compulsory|end=Saturday morning (EST)|msg=I won't be on for Saturday the 25th, though.}}


