{{Documentation subpage}}
=== Usage === Use this to show your kindness on Christmas or your evilness on Halloween. Just insert on your user page on those days and fill in the forms.
=== Parameters === Most of the time it looks like this:
{{HappyHolidays}}
That's from: <nowiki>{{HappyHolidays}}</nowiki>
However you must set an add and a signature like this:
<nowiki>{{HappyHolidays|[Holiday image]|[Holiday Name]|[Your User Name}}</nowiki>
It comes out with this:
{{HappyHolidays||Holiday Name|[[User:Downdate|Your User Name]]}}
End result:
{{HappyHolidays|Jack-o'-Lantern 2003-10-31.jpg|Halloween|''Downdate''}}
Of:
<nowiki>{{HappyHolidays|Jack-o'-Lantern 2003-10-31.jpg|Halloween|''Downdate''}}</nowiki>

